<!-- wedding party -->
<div id="weddingparty" class="panel">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-6" style="border-right: 2px solid #999;">
        <div class="media">
          <span class="circularmaria pull-right"></span>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h3 class="media-heading">The Bride</h3>
          With a passion for fine arts and finer food, Maria has spent her twenty six years cultivating her palette and cooking talents. A self-proclaimed "foodie", Maria pushes her culinary skills at every opportunity for friends and family. When not in the kitchen cooking up delicate cuisine Maria finds herself spending as much time as possible with her family, friends, and fiance. Maria loves being around others and always enjoys their company. You'll notice Maria's passions shine through on the wedding day as the venue and menu were carefully planned to reflect her style. 
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <div class="media">
          <span class="circularmike pull-left"></span>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h3 class="media-heading">The Groom</h3>
          A love of the outdoors, technology, and home improvement best describes Michael. Bouncing between the three seemingly unrelated activities, he still searches for time to spend with his close friends, family, and fiancee. When Mike isn't busy trying to program or hack together some new tech project, he's spending time working on the couples newly owned house, transforming it into their ideal dream home. Lately Michael has found a passion for camping and the outdoors and, if time and his fiancee allow, will spend the weekend biking and camping around New Jersey. 
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
        <div class="row" style="padding-top: 45px;">
      <div class="col-xs-6" style="border-right: 2px solid #999;">
        <div class="media">
          <span class="circularlisa pull-left"></span>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h3 class="media-heading">Maid of Honor</h3>
          Passing by the NYU labs late at night you may catch a glimpse of Lisa hard at work. Don't think for a moment though that she wouldn't gladly invite you to join her as Lisa always makes time for friends and family, putting them in the highest of regards. When not spending time with her husband or researching her way toward graduation, Lisa enjoys fine dining at local restaurants and you'll be sure her best friends will all be there. 
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <div class="media">
          <span class="circularasa pull-right"></span>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h3 class="media-heading">Best Man</h3>
          Best described as a wilderness astrophysicist, Asa enjoys all things science and exploring nature and its limits. When he's not catching a view of the night sky and its latest stars and planets Asa can be found biking every which way and studying for that next big college physics final. While not the social butterfly, Asa keeps his friends close and is always ready to give a helping hand at the drop of a bike wrench.
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
